snippet.title: Gatekeeper - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Gatekeeper is a new action game from Gravity Lagoon about fighting your way through enemy territory and finding the stolen Heart of the Universe. Learn more in the game's announcement trailer.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
